  "abstract": "The Board is publishing an interim rule amending Regulation E, which implements the Electronic Fund Transfer Act (EFTA). The EFTA establishes certain rights, liabilities, and responsibilities of participants involved in electronic fund transfers (EFTs) to and from consumer asset accounts. Among other things, the act and regulation require disclosures about the terms and conditions of EFT services, account activity, error resolution, and authorizations or confirmations concerning EFTs. These disc",
